Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磯貝佐奈子 十七歲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:05.80,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：佐奈子與早苗的前兩個音節發音一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直承蒙令兄關照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不是在哪裏見過？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是個小鎮 或許曾在路上有遇見過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明這麼漂亮 竟然會跟哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟會跟哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太可憐了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好嗎 芽衣沒發現是早苗阿姨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.60,0:00:34.66,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 放開她啊我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:36.60,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你請放開她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也大吃一驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:39.72,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:42.00,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 小心我告媽媽去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間差點都認不出來是媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是有種似曾相識的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春原同學打算去哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之應該是先去吃飯什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他知道什麼有格調的餐廳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 渚 這地方之前是幹什麼的來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 很抱歉我不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…佐奈子小姐 肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 附近有家我常去的店子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去吃個飯怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊 請帶我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏便是我常來的店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是家很不錯的店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推薦的是豬排蓋澆飯 我一日三餐都在吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:03:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是高檔餐廳 一般學生都基本不會進去的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽平君 你總是在這裏吃飯的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是豬排蓋澆飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 以我的身份來說這是必然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙款待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是總覺得這味道在哪兒嘗過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天只吃豬排蓋澆飯會營養不良的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後也請試著自己做做看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐奈子姐姐好溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明 明明是這麼溫柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然跟哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能不要這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來會去哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無非就是去看電影或購物之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 要是忽然被帶去打電動之類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是會很困擾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春原同學十分投入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（汝輸了）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊這機器 設定有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣哦 陽平君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種店子早點離開算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來去CD店 CD店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙對音樂的興趣好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了哦 這個是我非常喜歡的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的哥哥一塌糊塗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天色開始暗下來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:05:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚才剛剛開始呢 我們去能看到美麗夜景的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥還打算帶人家去逛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨再不回家是不是會很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 已經到了要準備晚飯的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙真礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都不能玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓我玩玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少煩人了 讓開啦 太礙事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.77,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開 你這傢伙 小心我打你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種程度沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩就是要打打鬧鬧的才會成長起來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別欺負我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來搞定了呢 那麼我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:05:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去情況好像有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請你等等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個孩子好像是出來幫忙買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果找不到回家的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哥哥找回去的路的時候 妹妹被那些男孩欺負了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想幫他們找回家的路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 他們能自己回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總 總之得先問問他們的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 衣服上有姓名牌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 背面還寫著住址
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 能回家了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中的要近真太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的家人非常高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就別慪氣了 快跟上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽平君 你生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是難得的一次約會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你還在說那種話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽平君 別再鬧彆扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要陽平君不介意 我是很願意再見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興你能如此重視和我在一起的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有時候還有更加重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要忘記這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 岡崎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有馬桶蓋子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺高興的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有馬桶蓋子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃豬排蓋澆飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有馬桶蓋子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很強的飯菜組合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但被早苗小姐說過的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飲食生活什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有馬桶蓋子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣昨晚也在擔心著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易交了個這麼好的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你本人卻還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確為了早苗小姐也要好好考慮一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有馬桶蓋子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了早苗小姐而在考慮著這種事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候夢想的職業有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球選手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛行員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被電到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬桶蓋子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論想成為哪個好像都很困難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上馬桶蓋子後 就連正常的對話也亂糟糟的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不要加不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你說要加的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 有說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 今天我不會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛中的男人是心胸開闊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心情真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 放學後她會打電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那樣啊 真的是迷上我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春原 我說你啊 也稍微替芽衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我和早苗小姐結婚 你和小渚結婚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是兄弟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教了 我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是起到反作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧 那個笨蛋興奮得不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣妹妹 你在等春原同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 他沒和你們在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼「如果女朋友打電話來沒接到就不好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 拿他沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能不要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 妹妹特地來看你 這態度不太合適吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在美妙的愛情面前 妹妹什麼的都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 戀愛真是美妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 芽衣你再不回去的話就不妙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我有必須去做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須去做的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 來看望我本來就是借口而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她從很久以前就憧憬著大都市 所以想在這裏玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裏有我喜歡的人 為了見他我才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜 喜歡的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前來的時候認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常成熟的人 教會了我很多玩法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還很溫柔 說我非常可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣 等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛真是美妙啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就要去見他了 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥也享受一下大人的戀愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣妹妹 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你也去追她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 唔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但早苗小姐要是打電話過來該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼還在說這種話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果對方是個壞人該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但戀愛是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你很生氣 但那樣說也有點過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦 這樣只會使事情更加複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看到那樣的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他馬上追出來說「別到那種人那裏去」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被打被罵也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已經做好那種準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明希望他來罵我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候常常被附近的男孩子弄哭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那時哥哥總會站出來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要一哭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥就一定會飛奔過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「不要惹芽衣哭」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很令人安心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了中學後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球踢得越來越好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不單是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球隊上下都覺得他很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的哥哥不是真正的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見女孩子被欺負了 哥哥是不會視而不見的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也應該會擔心我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡崎哥 哥哥的女朋友其實是假冒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就知道肯定會穿幫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 春原同學的女朋友是我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉騙了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿他沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大家添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們並沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿他沒有辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也和春原去約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 算是上次的重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經不用化妝也可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺已經喜歡上了這身裝扮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 都在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眼就看出是媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋生 這身裝扮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 噓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓的說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 你們在打什麼壞主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在練習舞台劇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台劇？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:15:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 然後想讓早苗阿姨來幫忙排演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這不都是些女裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨 別管這些趕快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.41,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿成這樣能上舞台嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:15.97,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 現在還在策劃中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因為害羞而逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 她永遠都是這麼容易害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這次是什麼樣的劇本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這次還是由渚主持的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在好像遇到了瓶頸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話幫她想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就去找早苗阿姨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好見面的地方不是這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是打算跟著早苗阿姨的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過既然是早苗阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給她也應該沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去哪裏玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直擔心著春原 也會很累的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很合適芽衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果岡崎哥真的是我的哥哥就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這麼想的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就試著像對待哥哥一樣對待我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像對待哥哥一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說哦 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 比想像的還有破壞力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 禁止說哥哥二字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 不能叫哥哥的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是別停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…是從什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓芽衣妹妹叫你哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特別的興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡…岡崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的 這是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們什麼都沒有看見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻氣會傳染的 快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是禁止叫哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還是不禁止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣到底怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}還是要禁止 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 這麼多的種類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大都市就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也不算什麼大都市
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒有看到過這種樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主可麗餅…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真的沒有看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 價格也是公主級的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子可真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不換別的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這邊的 領主可麗餅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣好想吃公主可麗餅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我這個人可真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃的話也給你吃一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就吃一口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 把草莓吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說可以吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最討厭哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 別討厭我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一起去拍那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣我就原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢 傻兮兮的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請選擇您喜歡的背景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---D---
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看 這個不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 要開始拍攝了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:18:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞死人了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡崎哥 記得貼在學生證上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會去貼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 你到哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見女朋友去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們才是在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼 我們不就是在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哥哥沒有關係 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 終於還是被發現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你想的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣的男朋友就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 那小渚怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我會和她分手的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實昨晚芽衣是住我那裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是啊 芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 是和岡崎哥單獨相處的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼走吧 芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是…就這個樣子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓他擔心一下 所以就信口開河了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 為了我們而…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都這樣去挑撥他了 也沒什麼反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為他會展現一下什麼叫作可靠的哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大概覺得我無論怎麼樣都無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒有這樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但說謊還是不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣 再不回去的話就不妙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都整整一個星期沒有上學 家裏人也會擔心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子是不能回去的 如果哥哥不能振作起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡崎哥 我還是想讓哥哥再去踢足球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始踢足球的話 一定會變回以前的那個哥哥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.05,0:21:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能的話讓哥哥再次回到足球部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想恐怕很難
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:22:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春原和足球部之間發生過什麼 芽衣你也是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得…只能這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了早苗的事情已經很忙了 沒空去管芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.41,0:23:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣 還是再重新考慮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.00,0:23:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有很多優點 只是不善於表現出來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.90,0:24:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打架啊 岡崎

